    {
      "id": "d40d1eb6-1d66-442d-a450-3a2f1bd4cf9a",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The main aim of the study is to predict the success of first-year undergraduate students. Authors extract multiple features from both the SIS and LMS as well: socio-demographics, origin, previous qualifications and educational path. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "d40d1eb6-1d66-442d-a450-3a2f1bd4cf9a",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
          "page_id": "fd6153cf-0a1c-4664-9a99-74f4264d7d8e"
        },
        "created_time": "2024-08-02T17:16:00.000Z",
        "last_edited_time": "2024-08-02T17:34:00.000Z",
