    {
      "id": "28df8b56-73ad-4268-8921-4520a7fdacd6",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Authors use 3 distinct moments of prediction: before start of year, end of first semester and after second semester, with SVM achieving the best overall performance.",
